# Help: VFIO userspace device driver framework (SPDK, DPDK)
#
# VFIO plus the generic PCI VFIO bus driver. The /dev/vfio container and
# the type1 IOMMU backend (VFIO_CONTAINER, VFIO_IOMMU_TYPE1) come via the
# Kconfig select chain on x86/arm64 when IOMMUFD is not forced on. Needs
# an IOMMU driver layered on (core/iommu-pci.config on x86,
# arch/arm64.config on arm64) plus a guest vIOMMU, or VFIO no-IOMMU mode.
# See: drivers/vfio/Kconfig
CONFIG_VFIO=m
CONFIG_VFIO_PCI=m
